reviews.review_description:
I am in LOVE, totally looking forward to what's to come in the future! The developer is a really sweet and cool dude too. The game has AI that is actually aware of you and doesn't drive like you're not there, a lot of fairly fun tracks, people have complained about the handling which turned out to be a bug and is actually getting fixed (now for real) in the most recent update so now you can't spin out as easily as you could. I seriously encourage you to give this game a try, I've had a lot of fun ^^

I have no idea what to say please try it ;~;

I promise it's good
